Interface IWrappedOWLOntologyManagerChangeListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
ClassHierarchyTreeContentProvider, ClassHierarchyView, OntologyManagerTableContentProvider, OntologyManagerView
public interface IWrappedOWLOntologyManagerChangeListener

Any listener wanting to listen to loading and removing ontologies from WrappedOWLOntologyManagers have to implement this interface.

Author:
Philipp Nolte
